@cmd_F1 $POD_SSH "hexa run /workspace/anima/serving/serve_alm_14b.hexa --ckpt /workspace/ckpt_alm_14b_r10c_seed3407/step_2000 --port 8080 &"
@gate_expected_F1 service binds :8080; $POD_SSH "curl -s localhost:8080/health" returns {"status":"ok",...}. Takes 30-60s for model load.
