# ============================================================================
# PITFALLS (lessons baked in from prior collapse)
# ============================================================================
@pitfall SENTINEL_NOT_CALLED r10 inline ASCII-only collapse_score missed 녕녕녕녕 — r10c uses kr_gen_sentinel.hexa subprocess (E7-OSS-01). D1 line `sentinel-hexa /workspace/anima/training/kr_gen_sentinel.hexa` is LOAD-BEARING.
@pitfall WATCHER_FALSE_TRAINING r10 watcher reported TRAINING after trainer death for hours — r10_watcher.hexa now has pid_alive() gate (E7-OSS-02). D2 TRAIN_PID env var is LOAD-BEARING.
@pitfall EARLY_LOSS_TOO_GOOD loss<1.0 before step 500 = collapse in 14B LoRA fresh-init. r10c inline gate (E7-OSS-03) forces sentinel if triggered. Do NOT interpret fast loss drop as convergence without C3/E1 PASS.
@pitfall MFS_QUOTA torch.save during training silently partials. A3 preflight + save_every>=2000 (per training/CLAUDE.md runpod_mfs_quota) prevents. Do NOT run in-training rclone.
@pitfall CORPUS_OOM local kowiki read_file(1.28 GiB) blows 4GB RSS. kowiki_slice.hexa uses head|awk pipe (CORPUS-OSS-01). Don't bypass with read_file on pod either.
@pitfall HEXA_BINARY_ARCH hexa binary this session was macOS Mach-O — Linux host can write .hexa source but not execute. Run all hexa commands on pod or macOS host.

